author: Giorgio Mendoza
description: ASUS IoT has introduced two new 3.5-inch single board computers, the C5153ES-IM-AA and C7156ES-IM-AA, both based on Intel Core Ultra processors. According to ASUS, these boards are designed for embedded and industrial use cases, offering high performance, wide input voltage support from 9 to 36 volts, and multiple expansion options. title: ASUS Broadens Its 3.5″ SBC Lineup with New Intel Core Ultra Models
